      "content": "but that's just more noise... more \"people\" and more \"support\" and more \"walking through hell.\" that's exactly what i'm trying to escape. i don't want to walk through hell, i just want to stop being in it. it feels like there's no middle ground. it's either this constant, crushing cycle or just... making it all be over. like, there has to be a way to just end the struggle without it being some big, dramatic thing. just peace. don't you see how much easier it would be for everyone if i just wasn't a burden anymore?",
